In the MATTER OF the License of Cheryl ACKERMAN, M.D., License No. 25MA06096100 to Practice Medicine and Surgery in the State of New Jersey M-1184/1185 September Term 2017
080161 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 21, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion of Cheryl Ackerman for leave to proceed as an indigent (M-1184) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion to vacate the order of dismissal and reinstate the notice of petition for certification (M-1185) is denied.
